Benchmark on Random Graph Generation

George G. Vega Yon

2018-07-06

Source: vignettes/benchmarks.Rmd
benchmarks.Rmd

Erdos Renyi

ans100 <- microbenchmark(
  igraph    = sample_gnp(100, .05, directed = FALSE),
  randgraph = rgraph_er_gnp(100, .05),
  times = 1e3,
  unit = "relative"
)

ans100
#> Unit: relative
#>       expr      min       lq     mean  median       uq      max neval
#>     igraph 9.657407 8.960962 10.44058 8.51825 8.188433 65.39098  1000
#>  randgraph 1.000000 1.000000  1.00000 1.00000 1.000000  1.00000  1000
